# =================== Email on linux ===============
1. sudo apt-get install php-mail
2. sudo apt-get install sendmail
3. sudo sendmailconfig
4.

# ================= Transfer file ==================
1. apt-get install netcat (deploy server)
2. nc -l -p 1234 > out.file (deploy server)
3. nc -w 3 [destination] 1234 < out.file